{
  "stem": "14737.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in the passport is already written, Jude.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You cannot take it out from the passport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would [INAUDIBLE] the passport without Jude-- without Jude, somehow, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We will think of something else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But here is already, with this passport, I can do nothing-- as far as to get out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One day, I decided finally, I cannot stay here, I'm going back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm going to back Hungary, I'll go on the train, and what's going to happen is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had another friend by the name of Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Goldstein.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He just did get his doctorate in medicine before Hitler came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We're going, coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Finally, one train, another train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We're coming to the border, smuggled in ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We're going to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We came to Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in Bratislava's already good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're going there to the Jewish community, getting some meals, some advice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they start to say to us also, you're going back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What are you going to Hungary?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Finally we decided to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Coming back to Hungary to a border, a certain border-- the police, the Germans, the Slovakian, let us out, and the Hungarians come and chase us down from the train.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You are not-- you are Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Chase down from the train in a field.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, the train was stopped at the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm going to be in a field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You cannot come into Hungary, you don't-- you don't have a entry visa.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't have-- you are not a citizen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Despite we show we are from Dovhoje.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Ah, it doesn't mean nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we wait.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Comes another train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The police are again-- those-- these are the border, they're the custom borders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To make a long story short, we smuggle in ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
